Ok we all know what happened everyone knows what happened so why at this point in time with all the evidence that’s out there and the timing couldn’t be more perfect to just throw it all out there for the whole world to see so that every news outlet no matter how hard they try cannot spin it to there best ability why hasn’t it been done yet. I mean they would really be doing the country a great disservice if this wasn’t shown to the country before we go vote in Nov. what an opportunity to create an absolute landslide this makes watergate look like a parking ticket for God’s sake. If this doesn’t come to fruition then I don’t think the trump campaign really wants to be re-elected what a waste......Echoed
